Title: Windows Phone 7 Bing Maps CloudMade TileSource Sample
Description:
This project is designed to be a sample of how you can use Custom map tiles provided by CloudMade.com in the Bing Maps Windows Phone 7 Control. 

This give you the benefit of using one of the many thousands of pre created map styles at CloudMade.com or creating your own map style
